cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for autonomous driving, specifically in the context of camera-based sensors. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of these techniques in robotics (cs.RO), and the use of generative models (GANs) for data augmentation (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the paper mentions the impact of soiling on the processing of images, which could be considered a security and privacy issue (cs.CR).
